name: NFTboxHEN 01
description:
Introducing NFTboxHEN, where we release an NFT-filled grab bag w/amazing, international artists. Each edition features 1 artist in particular for the core box concept. Each box is a low-priced 1/1 ed. in comparison to the value of all the NFTs inside. Welcome to @NFTboxHen 📦

This is a one-time, NFT grab bag that, once purchased, content will be sent to the buyer and detached. Then the box is empty and becomes a cool collectible itself.

💎 EDITION 01
🎨 3 pieces by Qubyt
🎨 1 piece by GummyLSD
🎨 1 piece by Fabi Yamada


📦 Don't miss a drop! Follow us: https://twitter.com/NFTboxHen
